_sText:
This was created as my very first Hammer project (I literally just learned how to use the program earlier today), so I understand that it's a bit bland and simple. However, I hope that at least someone out there can download it and have a bit of fun. Any suggestions are welcome!

I've marked the map as being in the Beta stage because there are a few things I've not yet implemented (or learned how to use, for that matter).
